text: Saving Yusuf is the 7th mixtape by American rapper Stalley. It was released on January 25, 2016. ==Track listing== ;Sample credits * "Came A Long Way" contains elements of "Chanson d'Un Jour d'Hiver" performed by Alain Mion & Cortex. ==References== Category:2016 mixtape albums Category:Maybach Music Group albums Category:Albums produced by FKi (production team)
title: Saving Yusuf
